import Header from "./homework33-34/Header/Header"
import Main from "./homework33-34/Main/Main"
import NavBar from "./homework33-34/NavBar/NavBar"
import ArticleSection from "./homework33-34/ArticleSection/ArticleSection"
import VoteForSmile from "./homework33-34/VoteForSmile/VoteForSmile"
import Home from "./homework33-34/Home/Home"
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom"

export default function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <>
        <Header />
        <Main>
          <NavBar />
          <ArticleSection>
            <Routes>
              <Route
                path="/homework33-react"
                element={<Home />}
              />
              <Route
                path="/homework33-react/VoteForSmile"
                element={<VoteForSmile />}
              />
            </Routes>
          </ArticleSection>
        </Main>
      </>
    </Router>
  )
}
